    <item>
      <title>Diamondback 为 Endeavour 交易出售 55 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/diamondback-kicks-off-bond-sale-to-help-fund-endeavor-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Diamondback Energy Inc. 在美国投资级市场借款 55 亿美元，为其以 260 亿美元收购 Endeavor Energy Resources LP 提供部分资金，与其他蓝筹公司一起利用强劲的投资者需求进行与收购相关的债务交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/diamondback-kicks-off-bond-sale-to-help-fund-endeavor-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在 CPI 数据公布之前，新兴股市攀升至 2022 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/emerging-stock-index-heads-for-highest-close-in-nearly-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股市收于 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平，交易员正在为本周的美国通胀数据做好准备，以衡量美联储下一步的货币政策举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/emerging-stock-index-heads-for-highest-close-in-nearly-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:45:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
